{"word":"ἀνακρεμάννυμι","slug":"ἀνακρεμάννυμι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνακρεμάννυμι</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to hang up on</i> a thing, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; <el>ἐς . .</el> or <el>πρός. . .</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be hung up</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to make dependent</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}